{
  "page": "Alton Greyjoy",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Greyjoy\" title=\"House Greyjoy\"><img alt=\"House Greyjoy.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/5b/House_Greyjoy.svg/50px-House_Greyjoy.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/5b/House_Greyjoy.svg/75px-House_Greyjoy.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/5b/House_Greyjoy.svg/100px-House_Greyjoy.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Lord</span><br />Alton Greyjoy<br /><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> the Holy Fool</span></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Greyjoy\" title=\"House Greyjoy\"><img alt=\"House Greyjoy.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/5b/House_Greyjoy.svg/50px-House_Greyjoy.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/5b/House_Greyjoy.svg/75px-House_Greyjoy.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/5b/House_Greyjoy.svg/100px-House_Greyjoy.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Alias</th><td>\nThe Holy Fool</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Titles</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_the_Iron_Islands\" title=\"Lord of the Iron Islands\">Lord of the Iron Islands</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Reaper_of_Pyke\" title=\"Lord Reaper of Pyke\">Lord Reaper of Pyke</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Greyjoy\" title=\"House Greyjoy\">House Greyjoy</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Ironborn\" title=\"Ironborn\">ironborn</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Alton Greyjoy</b>, known as the <b>Holy Fool</b>, was a <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_the_Iron_Islands\" title=\"Lord of the Iron Islands\">Lord of the Iron Islands</a> and head of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Greyjoy\" title=\"House Greyjoy\">House Greyjoy</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_the_old_way_and_the_new.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_the_old_way_and_the_new.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Alton_Greyjoy&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>According to Archmaester <a href=\"/index.php/Haereg\" title=\"Haereg\">Haereg</a>'s <i><a href=\"/index.php/History_of_the_Ironborn\" title=\"History of the Ironborn\">History of the Ironborn</a></i>, Alton wanted to conquer new lands beyond the <a href=\"/index.php/Lonely_Light\" title=\"Lonely Light\">Lonely Light</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_the_old_way_and_the_new.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_the_old_way_and_the_new.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> but no one has ever successfully crossed the <a href=\"/index.php/Sunset_Sea\" title=\"Sunset Sea\">Sunset Sea</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> with the possible exception of <a href=\"/index.php/Elissa_Farman\" title=\"Elissa Farman\">Elissa Farman</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Alton_Greyjoy&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_the_old_way_and_the_new.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_the_old_way_and_the_new.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_the_old_way_and_the_new.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Iron Islands: The Old Way and the New.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/index.php/So_Spake_Martin\" title=\"So Spake Martin\">So Spake Martin</a>: <a class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.westeros.org/Citadel/SSM/Entry/Trade_with_Asshai\">Trade with Asshai (August 26, 2000)</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, The Long Reign - Jaehaerys and Alysanne: Policy, Progeny, and Pain.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks hlist mw-collapsible mw-collapsed collapsible autocollapse navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;width:100%;color:inherit;;;\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\";\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><div class=\"plainlinks hlist\" style=\"display:block;float:left;font-weight:normal;font-size:88%;padding-top:3px;text-align:left;width:6.8em;\"><ul><li class=\"nv-view\"><a href=\"/index.php/Template:Lords_of_the_Iron_Islands\" title=\"Template:Lords of the Iron Islands\"><span title=\"View this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">v</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-talk\"><a href=\"/index.php?title=Template_talk:Lords_of_the_Iron_Islands&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Template talk:Lords of the Iron Islands (page does not exist)\"><span title=\"Discuss this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">d</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-edit\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://awoiaf.westeros.org/index.php?title=Template:Lords_of_the_Iron_Islands&amp;action=edit\"><span title=\"Edit this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">e</span></a></li></ul></div><div class=\"\" style=\"font-size:110%;\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_the_Iron_Islands\" title=\"Lord of the Iron Islands\">Lords of the Iron Islands</a></div></th></tr><tr style=\"height:2px;\"><td></td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\";;\">Official succession<br />From <a href=\"/index.php/House_Greyjoy\" title=\"House Greyjoy\">House Greyjoy</a></td><td style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Vickon_Greyjoy\" title=\"Vickon Greyjoy\">Vickon</a> (2-33)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Goren_Greyjoy\" title=\"Goren Greyjoy\">Goren</a> (33-?)</li>\n<li>Dalton's father (≤113-128)<sup>1</sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Dalton_Greyjoy\" title=\"Dalton Greyjoy\">Dalton</a> (128-133)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Toron_Greyjoy\" title=\"Toron Greyjoy\">Toron</a> (133-?)</li>\n<li><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Alton</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Torwyn_Greyjoy\" title=\"Torwyn Greyjoy\">Torwyn</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Loron_Greyjoy_(lord)\" title=\"Loron Greyjoy (lord)\">Loron</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Dagon_Greyjoy\" title=\"Dagon Greyjoy\">Dagon</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Quellon_Greyjoy\" title=\"Quellon Greyjoy\">Quellon</a> (?-283)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Balon_Greyjoy\" title=\"Balon Greyjoy\">Balon</a> (283-299)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Euron_Greyjoy\" title=\"Euron Greyjoy\">Euron</a> (299-Present)</li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr style=\"height:2px\"><td></td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\";;\">Claimants to the Seastone Chair</td><td style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-even\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Rodrik_Greyjoy_(son_of_Dalton)\" title=\"Rodrik Greyjoy (son of Dalton)\">Rodrik Greyjoy</a> (133-?)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Sam_Salt\" title=\"Sam Salt\">Sam Salt</a> (133-?)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Asha_Greyjoy\" title=\"Asha Greyjoy\">Asha Greyjoy</a> (299-Present)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Theon_Greyjoy\" title=\"Theon Greyjoy\">Theon Greyjoy</a> (299-Present)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Victarion_Greyjoy\" title=\"Victarion Greyjoy\">Victarion Greyjoy</a> (299-Present)</li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr style=\"height:2px;\"><td></td></tr><tr><td class=\"navbox-abovebelow\" style=\";\" colspan=\"2\"><div>\n<ul><li><sup>1</sup> Lord Dalton's father is known to have been the heir of Pyke when Dalton was young. Therefore he could not have been Lord of the Iron Islands before 113 AC, the year of Dalton's birth.</li></ul>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403175130\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.102 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.313 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 976/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 17613/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 18079/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 4821/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 17/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 2235/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.190/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.48 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  299.206      1 -total\n 93.46%  279.631      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 92.77%  277.569      1 Template:Infobox\n 10.73%   32.097     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  5.31%   15.893      5 Template:Infobox_label\n  3.10%    9.268      1 Template:Lords_of_the_Iron_Islands\n  2.93%    8.756      1 Template:Navbox\n  2.46%    7.363      3 Template:Ref\n  1.56%    4.659      3 Template:Ref/core\n  1.29%    3.871      1 Template:Navbar\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:18918-0!canonical and timestamp 2026040317513